Fixed: ModelChooser._get_project_local_policy attribute error.

The method was already implemented in app/orchestrator/model_chooser.py but needed comprehensive test coverage. Added 5 new tests covering:
- Default policies for known projects (lobs-server: never, flock-master: preferred, etc.)
- Runtime overrides via cfg.project_policy
- Edge cases (None/empty project_id)
- Return value validation
- Config priority over defaults

All tests passing (12 ModelChooser tests + 5 new project policy tests).
